     <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
      <div class="card-header bg-warning text-dark">
<h5 class="mb-0">?? Important Notes</h5>
  </div>
      <div class="card-body">
   <ul class="mb-0">
 <li><strong>In-Memory:</strong> All data is stored in RAM. Restart clears everything (unless auto-loaded)</li>
  <li><strong>No Dev Servers:</strong> This platform is your dev environment for database testing</li>
     <li><strong>Plato Changes Only:</strong> Only Plato (internal DB) can be modified locally</li>
      <li><strong>Migration Scripts:</strong> Always generate scripts before applying changes to real Plato</li>
    <li><strong>Test First:</strong> Validate all changes in this environment before production</li>
  </ul>
